reviewText: DO NOT BUY! Big x fan and was very dissapointed. Only the first 2 tracks worled on the cd. Like the rest wasn't even in there. Contwcted seller. Seller will not respond. this product is a scam. What a piece of garbage. Seller better fix this problem!
Love the music video and the live concert.  Hope that  DMX with have a sucessful return to the music industry.
